INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('208', '1', '2013-09-05 11:07:26', '2013-09-05 11:07:26', '<h1>South King County Car Collision Attorneys</h1>\r\n\r\n<strong>Kent Personal Injury Attorneys<strong>\r\n\r\nFor over 40 years, the Levinson Law Offices have countered the outrageous treatment our clients receive from insurance companies. Bill Levinson â the founder of our firm â focuses on aggressive advocacy on behalf of clients and their family members dealing with life-changing vehicle collisions of all types, slip and fall, to the more devastating brain, neck and spinal cord injuries. He shows his compassion and dedication by keeping himself accessible throughout the entire course of a case.\r\n\r\nIn the hours and days following an collision, many victims are not sure what to do. Insurance adjusters call almost immediately, wanting vital information to secure a quick settlement. They claim to be on the side of the injured party. In reality, their goal is much different.\r\n\r\nFrankly, if insurance companies were truly looking out for collision victims, attorney Bill Levinson would not be needed. He established the Levinson Law Offices in 1973 to even the odds his clients face in fending off the intimidating tactics of insurers. Instead of paying fair compensation, they fund lobbying efforts to demonize injured parties, labeling them and grieving family members greedy.\r\n\r\nKent Personal Injury Lawyers\r\n\r\nCollision victims in the state of Washington face a harsh reality. Doctors, insurance providers and big money lobbyists have spent vast sums of money demonizing them. They question their patriotism. They allege that greed, not pain and suffering motivate them to file a claim. Whiplash â a legitimately serious injury â has become a four-letter word.\r\n\r\nIn personal injury claims, money is the only justice the system can provide. Compensation is the sole option and best outcome. It sends the strongest message to insurance companies wrongfully denying legitimate claims and employing bad faith practices. It holds negligent individuals and companies responsible for inattentiveness and recklessness in accidents that involve:\r\n\r\n    Car accidents\r\n    Truck accidents\r\n    Bicycle accidents\r\n    Motorcycle accidents\r\n    Pedestrian accidents\r\n    Premises liability\r\n    Dog bites and animal attacks\r\n\r\n\r\nFor more information about Mr. Levinson\'s background and qualifications, please follow the link below to review his profile or contact our Kent office at 253-854-7440 or toll free at 206-234-1269. You can also e-mail us to schedule an appointment.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-05 11:07:26', '2013-09-05 11:07:26', '', '29', 'http://brentbowen.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/29-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
