INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('329', '1', '2013-10-23 10:51:22', '2013-10-23 10:51:22', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Criminal Defense After a Texas Drug Arrest</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/B6ImImUX-bw?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\nWhen you have been arrested for a drug crime in Texas, your future and your freedom could be at stake. Working with a criminal defense lawyer you feel comfortable with â someone who truly understands the issues involved â can help you achieve positive results.\r\n\r\nAttorney Brent BowenÂ is a former Denton County assistant district attorney who now handles criminal defense cases. He provides understanding and effective legal representation for people accused of crimes involving a wide range of drugs including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Marijuana</li>\r\n	<li>Crack / cocaine</li>\r\n	<li>Methamphetamine</li>\r\n	<li>Heroin</li>\r\n	<li>Cheese</li>\r\n	<li>Prescription narcotics / pain killers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nUnder his guidance, our firm effectively handles drug possession arrest cases and other drug crimes including drug trafficking, growing and distributing illegal substances, and selling drugs. If you have been arrested for any of these crimes,Â contact usÂ today to speak with a drug crime defense attorney.\r\n\r\nEach drug arrest involves unique facts and laws. TheÂ Bowen Law GroupÂ stays up to date on the most recent changes in the law, so we can use our in-depth knowledge to your advantage. Whether your drug arrest involved a violation of search and seizure laws, drug and gun charges for carrying a concealed weapon, or issues ofÂ juvenile law, we can help.\r\n<h3>Talking About Addiction</h3>\r\nThe Bowen Law Group focuses on understanding clients, not just their cases. This means that we often look beyond the immediate legal issue, like a drug possession arrest, to the things that are really affecting you. Sometimes, this means talking to you about addiction.\r\n\r\nFrequently, a first drug possession arrest â or a second one â means hitting bottom. It can be a difficult time. Clients can benefit by addressing issues of drug abuse and addiction. We help refer clients to treatment programs. We recommend chemical dependency evaluations and counseling.\r\n<h3>Contact Bowen Law Group for a Free Initial Consultation</h3>\r\nTo talk about your drug possession arrest with an attorney at Bowen Law Group, pleaseÂ contactÂ our Denton, Texas law office at 940-566-0606. We answer our phones 24 hours a day, 7 days a week so you can get quick responses to your legal concerns â especially when an arrest has put your freedom at stake.', 'Drug Crimes', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'drug-crimes', '', '', '2013-10-23 10:51:22', '2013-10-23 10:51:22', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=329', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('330', '1', '2013-10-23 10:51:48', '2013-10-23 10:51:48', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Legal Representation After an Arrest for a Theft Crime</h2>\r\nWhether it resulted from an error in judgment, a false accusation or another situation entirely, an arrest for a theft crime should be taken seriously. And the first step to a serious criminal defense is to work with a knowledgeable and experienced attorney.\r\n\r\nOurÂ criminal defenseÂ lawyer â Brent Bowen â is a former Denton County assistant district attorney who knows the law and who focuses on providing strong and effective criminal defense.\r\n\r\nOur Denton, Texas, law firm handles a broad range of felony and misdemeanor theft crimes in Texas state courts. Regardless of the allegations you face, we can talk openly with you about building a strong criminal defense:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Robbery and aggravated robbery</li>\r\n	<li>Burglary</li>\r\n	<li>Shoplifting</li>\r\n	<li>Embezzlement / employee theft</li>\r\n	<li>Auto theft</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Search and Seizure Issues</h3>\r\nEach arrest is unique, but most arrests for theft crimes involve some issues related to search and seizure. WhenBowen Law GroupÂ handles your case, we always check to make sure that police followed the letter of the law.\r\n\r\nThe law on search and seizure is constantly changing as existing laws are applied in new situations. The attorneys at Bowen Law Group stay current on the law so that we can offer quality representation to our clients.\r\n\r\nOur law firm philosophy is based on understanding our clients as people, not just as cases. Other issues, like financial hardship, drug or alcohol dependence, are often behind an arrest for a theft crime. As attorneys and counselors, we help you get the support you need for those issues â in addition to providing a strong and effective criminal defense in Texas courts.\r\n<h3>Contact Bowen Law Group</h3>\r\nTo talk about your criminal defense with an attorney at Bowen Law Group, pleaseÂ contactÂ our Denton, Texas, law office at 940-566-0606. Our phones are answered 24 hours a day, seven days a week so you can get quick responses to your legal concerns â especially when you need them most.', 'Theft, Burglary, Robbery', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'theft-burglary-robbery', '', '', '2013-10-23 10:51:48', '2013-10-23 10:51:48', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=330', '0', 'page', '', '0');
