INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('383', '1', '2013-10-23 12:06:52', '2013-10-23 12:06:52', 'CHRYSANDRA BOWEN: You will typically find people fighting over child custody inÂ family lawÂ cases. That includes visitation, possession, and child support. Behind that, youâre going to find people fighting over other assets, which would mostly be money. How is the money going to be split and any property that they have?\r\n\r\nChild custodyÂ can be determined either by status quo, which is what is the situation at the time of separation. Or when you go into court, the courtâs going to look more at whoâs the primary parent doing the primary roles for the child. The one piece of advice I often give my clients is that they have to push emotions aside. You have to focus on moving on with your life and dividing up your assets. If there are children involved, itâs more important that you focus on their needs than your own.\r\n\r\nThe thing that I enjoy about family law is that I can step into someoneâs shoes that is very emotional and not able to focus on the actual legal aspects of a marriage. Itâs easy for me to push that aside and negotiate for them for whatâs fair. Fair is not always what everyone thinks it is. But itâs what the law will allow you. If youâre experiencing a family law matter, you should hire Bowen Law Group because we understand our clients, not just their cases.', 'Family Law Video Transcript', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'family-law-video-transcript', '', '', '2013-10-23 12:06:52', '2013-10-23 12:06:52', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=383', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('384', '1', '2013-10-23 12:07:11', '2013-10-23 12:07:11', 'BRENT BOWEN: At theÂ Bowen Law Group, we handle all types of criminal cases, from traffic tickets,Â DWIs,Â drug cases, assaults, anywhere from attempted murder to murder charges.\r\n\r\nIâve been practicing criminal law for nearly 10 years. Iâve worked in county attorneysâ offices, district attorneysâ offices, as well as being in private practice for a number of years. Working for a district attorneyâs office is I believe a benefit to my clients. I understand how things are processed through that office, which sometimes benefits my clients, where I might be able to head off a charge before itâs actually filed with the court.\r\n\r\nThere is no typical client that we deal with here at the Bowen Law Group. Itâs important when dealing with a client to understand whatâs going on in their lives and not just their criminal case. We try here at Bowen Law Group to get the clients the required counseling they may need or to benefit themselves as well as their case. Clients typically donât understand the severity of the matter that theyâre involved in. The range of punishment for offenses in Texas can be very different, depending on what type of charge they have. Itâs important for clients to understand when theyâre charged with a crime to immediately contact an attorney. They have certain rights that they need to protect. And they might not understand the criminal justice system.', 'Criminal Law Video Transcript', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'criminal-law-video-transcript', '', '', '2013-10-23 12:07:11', '2013-10-23 12:07:11', '', '0', 'http://brentbowen.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=384', '0', 'page', '', '0');
